(110, 3, '2013-11-13 09:19:40', '2013-11-13 09:19:40', '<b><span style="text-decoration: underline;"> </span></b>\n<p align="center"><b><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Nebel.TV – Media Entertainment for the Social Generation</span></b></p>\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>Have</b> you ever been speaking to one of your friends online and they let you know what they are about to watch or listen to…and you wish you had the latest Track, TV Episode or Movie?\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>Nebel.TV</b> brings together the entertainment needs of our contemporary society, eclectically blending together social networking and media sharing into a single, easy to use, user-friendly cutting edge mobile platform perfect for today’s social generation.\n\n&nbsp;\n<table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="left">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td valign="top" width="234"><em>Image courtesy of Ambro at FreeDigitalPhotos.net</em></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<b>With</b> Nebel.TV it’s now easier and more convenient, no matter when or wherever you are to share your media files with your friends. Now anyone with the Nebel.TV software can <i>freely gain instant access to the media files of their friends</i>. Choose what to watch or listen to by how the media is ranked, allowing you to stay up to date with the current trends and not get left out. Also there’s no need to fear that someone will steal your content,  integrated security gives you have full control - share only with those who are part of your social network. Along with the sharing security, the software also allows you to make your viewing activities private – nothing is shared unless you want it to be.\n\n&nbsp;\n<table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="left">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td valign="top" width="192"><em>Image courtesy of tungphoto at FreeDigitalPhotos.net</em></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<b>Nebel.TV</b> is so much more than a basic file sharing app, it allows you to see which media files are available for instant viewing as well as stream live broadcasts, pause and record for later playback, making it the perfect tool for the likes of commuters who don’t have time to finish what they’re watching. Take advantage of Nebel.TV’s inbuilt scalable encoding, to get around any network bandwidth or file formatting restrictions – smart technology means you’ll always access your file in the most convenient format possible.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>In</b> addition of viewing/listening to your favorite media file, those wanting to support their favorite artists or indeed any budding amateur without third party interference, Nebel.TV is a perfect source. Help in the promotion of up and coming artists, by pledging your support for their new projects both verbally and financially, thereby helping to get them recognized. Reward the artists themselves directly for their creativity not recording labels or hosting sites who all take a snatch off the royalties.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>The</b> software allows you to instantly pay and get paid for your own online content.\n\nNebel.TV incorporates a seamlessly integrated payment system without the need for credit cards, or other online payment services - this is especially useful for those who live in countries where the likes of Paypal™ are not supported.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>A</b> unique feature from the Nebel.TV platform means that with the integrated payment system  YOU now get paid for viewing online ads taking away the misery of ad bombardment and in-turn allowing you to spend the credit on your new content, everyone wins!\n\n&nbsp;\n<table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="left">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td valign="top" width="215"><em>Image courtesy of renjith krishnan at FreeDigitalPhotos.net</em></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<b>For</b> those budding artists striving to get their material distributed, then this is where Nebel.TV comes into its own. Get rewarded for your hard work and creativity as well as taking some of pain away from marketing your creations by targeting a global community. Require a more niche audience? Utilizing the social network aspect of the software will allow you to focus your distribution to a more targeted market. Know exactly where your material is being enjoyed the most - think of the possibilities of this, especially if you’re planning a series of gigs! Sell your audio and video projects, making use of Nebel.TV’s integrated payment system without giving away any of your master or performance royalties YOU keep 100% of YOUR royalties.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>You</b> don’t have to be a music artist to take advantage of Nebel.TV – why not create your own news or TV channel - broadcasting your own films and documentaries to your network. As your audience grows the more potential you have of receiving support for your projects or indeed maybe even get noticed by others in the industry.\n<table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="left">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td valign="top" width="187"><em>Image courtesy of digitalart at FreeDigitalPhotos.net</em></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\nThe potential and scope of Nebel.TV is huge, especially in today’s Social Media Generation, using cutting edge technology to revolutionize the way we socially network. Knowing how pricey new technology can be – one of Nebel.TV’s greatest <i>selling</i> points is that it is free!!!\n\n<b>Yes</b>, that’s right, but it doesn’t end there...remember, there is so much potential for making money too!! Let’s all join the social media revolution now by downloading the FREE software for your applicable device.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;', '', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', '110', '', '', '2013-11-13 09:19:40', '2013-11-13 09:19:40', '', 0, 'http://www.nebel.tv/?p=110', 0, 'post', '', 0),
