ize:11.0pt;\nfont-family:"Calibri","sans-serif";\nmso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-fareast-font-family:"Times New Roman";\nmso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;\nmso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\nmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;}\n</style><![endif]-->\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: ''Arial'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: black;">With</span></b><span style="font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: ''Arial'',''sans-serif''; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: black;"> Nebel.TV it’s now easier and more convenient, no matter when or wherever you are to share your media files with your friends. Now anyone with the Nebel.TV software can <i>freely gain instant access to the media files of their friends</i>. Choose what to watch or listen to by how the media is ranked, allowing you to stay up to date with the current trends and not get left out. Also there’s no need to fear that someone will steal your content,  integrated security gives you have full control - share only with those who are part of your social network. Along with the sharing security, the software also allows you to make your viewing activities private – nothing is shared unless you want it to be.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"></p>', 'Nebel.TV – Media Entertainment for the Social Generation', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'nebel-tv-media-entertainment-for-the-social-generation', '', '', '2013-11-13 09:51:25', '2013-11-13 09:51:25', '', 0, 'http://www.nebel.tv/?p=117', 0, 'post', '', 0),
