(186, 1, '2013-12-07 20:10:13', '2013-12-07 20:10:13', 'WHY?\r\nOver recent years the technology for Television sets has been increasing at a drastic rate – from the changeover to digital broadcast compliancy as opposed to the old analogue, higher definition sets, 3D compatibility for your home (who would have thought), even to internet ready (Smart) TVs.\r\n\r\nHowever the attempt of leading TV manufacturers to equip their TV sets with computer-like features such as web browsers and apps, currently struggle due to the lack of appropriate user controls, as well as ridiculously feeble CPUs leaving them remarkably mismatched to the outstanding capabilities of modern FullHD or UHD TV sets. Yet with this whole new world of cutting edge visual technology the content sources of the TV set remains basically unchanged. \r\n\r\nNebel.TV is a inspirational new free project aimed at revitalizing the World’s most common entertainment platform by creatively adapting existing technology and blending it social networking allowing for the evolution of how we use and enjoy our media in today’s mobile Social Generation.\r\n\r\nNebel.TV is here to address all of the TV-platform’s shortcomings, delivering a superior content quality by means of streamlining advanced peer-2-peer media sharing technologies alongside a user-interface utilizing social network ideology to be able share your media with those in your network easily, privately and securely.\r\n\r\nFor greater access Nebel.TV will be downloadable for free from Google Play directly to your tablet or phone giving you the freedom to enjoy access to your media whenever or wherever you wish, as well as being available in the neat convenient form of a HDMI dongle device (although this will not be needed to run the software on phones or tablets) for connection to your existing TV or home media library.\r\n\r\nThat’s right! The Nebel.TV platform will be downloadable for free, and what’s more, once you have the software, it’s also free to use - no subscription fees!!!\r\n\r\n\r\nHOW?\r\n\r\nNebel.TV aims to build its popularity from within internet communities, as we understand that the quickest way to gain public scrutiny/opinion is initially by opening up and promoting our project idea through these sources.\r\n\r\nNebel.TV’s distribution and use will be free as we believe the way in which we enjoy our media should be our, the viewer/listener’s choice, not decided upon by a committee.\r\n  \r\nCurrently we have used PayPal donation platform to start collecting funds. Later we will initiate our crowdfunding campaign in early May 2014. Using the crowdfunding platform allows YOU, the end user, to be a part of our dream, that being the evolution of how media should be enjoyed. Your donations will allow you to become part of the evolution, while we do the hard work using your money. We will have an in-depth blog <blog link> where you can actively follow our development progress, marketing campaigns as well as leave your comments and feedback on what you see.\r\n\r\nWe are currently working on a project demo to be exhibited to the sourcing crowd where we hope to secure the funds for our projected final product release in Q4 2014.\r\n\r\n\r\nWHO?\r\n\r\nNebel.TV is a project started early in 2013 by a group of 5 technology professionals each possessing over 15 years of development experience with different types of the software: traditional client-server, web, and mobile. Later the team has been expanded by 10+ more people spreading the team knowledge in other areas such as PR&marketing, media and entertainment platforms and law. \r\n\r\nIn August 2013, Nebel.TV has successfuly secured Seed 0 investment, from a reputable IT venture enterpreneur <insert link> and continued persuing it goal, to increase project awareness and get it to one of the crowd funding platforms.\r\n\r\nHere is the rogues gallery of Team Nebel.TV \r\n\r\nFEATURES\r\n\r\n1. Media Sharing – Sharing your media has now never been easier. Instant access to the media files of your friends. Keep full control over access to your own material, share only with those within your social circle.\r\n\r\n2. Enjoy both Live and Recorded content - Pause live broadcasts and continue watching whenever you choose, wherever you choose. Access the recorded content of your social network. Never miss anything again!\r\n\r\n3. Cutting edge technology for free - That’s right, pay absolutely nothing, zero, zilch, for the software download for your applicable device from the online store. Find out how we do this by visiting <link to article>\r\n\r\n4. Smart playback -  Instant media playback for audio or video (no waiting for your download) with automatic video downscaling on display or network restricted devices. Flattened peer-2-peer media files exchange architecture: no central tracking or storage servers required.\r\n\r\n5. Smoothly integrated payment system: Pay and get paid for your own online content - No credit cards required. Live in a country not supported by Paypal? Not a problem...the integrated Bitcoin system gives you the best confidentiality possible. Tired of being flooded with advertising...now GET paid to view ads and spent the credit on your new content!\r\n\r\n6. Support your favorite artists without third party intervention - Directly reward the artist themselves for their creativity, not the recording label, hosting sites etc. Heard or seen something that you enjoyed? Want to help get this artist recognised? Pledge your support to their future projects.\r\n\r\n7. An Artist yourself? A budding independent filmmaker or creative musician? Promote your content and receive 100% royalties for your work by reaching out to a global audience.\r\n\r\n\r\nRemember, we want to share our dream with you, your donations will allow us all to be part of an evolved Social Generation!!!\r\n', 'NEBEL.TV – At a Glance', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'nebel-tv-at-a-glance', '', '', '2013-12-07 20:10:20', '2013-12-07 20:10:20', '', 63, 'http://nebel.alexgal.info/?page_id=186', 0, 'page', '', 0),
